Package panels

Class GamePanel

java.lang.Object
java.awt.Component
java.awt.Container
javax.swing.JComponent
javax.swing.JPanel
panels.GamePanel
All Implemented Interfaces:
GameVariables, ImageObserver, MenuContainer, Serializable, Runnable, Accessible
public class GamePanel extends JPanel implements Runnable, GameVariables

GamePanel handles creating the screen and contains the main game loop. It also manages the top-level updating and rendering of all objects on the screen.

This class extends JPanel and implements Runnable and GameVariables.

Since:
February 24, 2024
Author:
Nick Clouse, Andrew Denegar, Molly O'Connor
